{"type": "article", "id": 64636, "title": "首部入围布克奖的图像小说，探讨互联网时代下的真理与信仰", "description": "这本书最令人好奇也是最重要的一点是：它讲述的并不是犯罪本身，而是一针见血地指出了真理与信仰的本质。在互联网时代的背景下，这两者都难逃被侵蚀的命运，更不用说是在特朗普统治下的当代美国了。——《卫报》", "date": "2019-10-10T07:37:11Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 52159, "name": "图像小说"}], "category": 5, "author": 589058, "comment_count": 6, "praise_count": 135, "image": "img/article/article_show/20191010144811TszQdp42lCAtBNo0.jpg", "contents": "<h3 nocleanhtml=\"true\">《消失的塞布丽娜》</h3><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20191010143631w83T9OWH51eUIroy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.210461\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>内容简介</h3><p class=\"\">塞布丽娜失踪了。某些人的生活也随之发生了剧变。一名美国空军士兵陷入了猜忌与阴谋组成的谜团，塞布丽娜的男友特迪变得精神恍惚、一蹶不振，她的妹妹桑德拉则在浑浑噩噩的等待中几欲抓狂……正当事件陷入迷局之时，一盒寄给报社的神秘录像带引发轩然大波。透过录像画面，人们窥见了一场真正的灾难……<br></p><h3>作者简介</h3><p class=\"\">尼克·德纳索（Nick Drnaso）， 1989 年出生于伊利诺伊州帕洛斯山市，是一位作家和图画小说家。他的第一本书《贝弗莉》获得了洛杉矶时报图书奖的最佳图像小说奖项；《消失的塞布丽娜》则是首部入围布克奖的图像小说的作品。现在他和妻子还有三只猫一起住在芝加哥。<br></p><h3>书籍摘录</h3><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20191010144147rDwTGbUsSWVnLIfJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.294698\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20191010144159UVQABkn9ZHg70avX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.293515\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20191010144212eL8Cd3AFO6hcJZ7q.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.291572\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20191010144224XD6WCrZILPqsiO0y.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.303653\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20191010144235HAcyO0IxEJMBwS84.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.296840\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20191010144246IMZ65V30KsgYSTUQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.268456\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20191010144258G452FlqegSKDHrRd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.296339\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20191010144310hkgYGSCmnyvu13Va.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.298981\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20191010144334G90MafDjcZWY235S.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.293515\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20191010144352s329N4A8WbklHto7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.287810\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20191010144413VUxYweHuSvyIjfaX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.291904\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20191010144424t8CTyPHv1me9AGNs.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.297511\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20191010144436DlGsviMXIp2d8HYQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.298746\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20191010144450kzOLmZwK671lNQ0o.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\"><br></p><p class=\"\">题图来自：《消失的塞布丽娜》</p>"}